- 'Repeated purchases' implies that the customer has placed more than one order.

- 'Cotopaxi size' refers to a standardized size value used by the brand Cotopaxi;
- 'Preferred size' is the size that a customer typically orders;
- 'Total orders' represents the sum of all order amounts for a customer.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.product_name) AS distinct_product_count
FROM orders o
JOIN products p ON o.product_id = p.product_id;

